<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Lectotype</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="71">
(designated here):-China, Tibet, Panggong Tso, July 25, 1927, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Bosshard s.n.</emphasis>
(Z000002688 digital image!, Figure 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Lectotype of S. pusilla Em. Schmid (Walter Bosshard, Bosshard s. n., Z 000002688)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.170.59527.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489393" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">5</figureCitation>
; Isolectotype: China, Tibet, Panggong Tso, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="71">Bosshard s.n.</emphasis>
, Z barcode Z000002689 and Z000002690 digital image!).
</paragraph>
